  "content": "\n \n \n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\">\n        <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"246\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb2R91xJQdibib12DocfyvQSVyW0eA0Zw35nEURZMibHJSjG0PoNyW8l1iav6Vh4par7tvwBeJj2PMVFaQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-imgfileid=\"505100885\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/208ae2bc-f951-4c83-eded-6c26fa225c00/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/208ae2bc-f951-4c83-eded-6c26fa225c00/public\"></span>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\">\n   <span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：定慧</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">还在用搜索和规则训练AI游戏？现在直接「看回放」学打宝可梦了！德州大学奥斯汀分校的研究团队用Transformer和离线强化学习打造出一个智能体，不靠规则、没用启发式算法，纯靠47.5万场人类对战回放训练出来，居然打上了Pokémon Showdown全球前10%！</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI 又有「新活」了！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">德州大学奥斯汀分校的研究团队用Transformers和离线强化学习训练出了一个宝可梦对战AI智能体，不但打法像人，还能在全球排名中杀进前 10%。</span></span></p>\n  <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0d7ca072-3398-406a-6ad6-cddd4e2b0900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5640625\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"640\" data-height=\"361\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"317\" data-imgfileid=\"505100869\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0d7ca072-3398-406a-6ad6-cddd4e2b0900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">论文地址：https://metamon.tech/</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">是的，你没看错，这不是那种靠搜索和规则的AI，而是靠人类历史对战数据「喂出来」的智能体，能自己学着打。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这个宝可梦游戏（全称Competitive Pokémon Singles）有多复杂呢？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在对战平台https://pokemonshowdown.com/上可以看到，即使不考虑策略，光是精灵、动作和物品的数量已经多到了非常夸张的程度（根本翻不完）。</span></span></p>\n  <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"453\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"516\" data-imgfileid=\"505100868\" data-ratio=\"0.80625\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9307271c-f24f-4785-58c1-a01ecf062e00/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" data-width=\"640\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9307271c-f24f-4785-58c1-a01ecf062e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着，AI要在信息不完全、策略博弈的环境中，把每一步出招、每一次换人，都当成下围棋一样来算。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">宝可梦对战融合了国际象棋般的长远策略规划、扑克牌那样充满未知信息和随机性，再加上足以填满一本百科全书的宝可梦、招式、特性和规则。玩家需要精心设计和操控自己的宝可梦队伍，击败对手的所有宝可梦才能获胜。这样一个充满不确定性、状态空间极其庞大的游戏，对AI来说是绝佳又极具挑战性的研究课题。</span></p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px 48px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种硬核程度，更像是宝可梦版的《星际争霸》。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">把「回放」喂给 AI，教它打宝可梦</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究团队开发了一个名为Metamon的平台，它使用来自Pokémon Showdown（以下简称PS）的人类游戏数据集来启用离线RL工作流。</span></span></p>\n  <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"262\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"2808\" data-imgfileid=\"505100874\" data-ratio=\"0.46574074074074073\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/35baeeb8-b582-405e-2f46-178de16f8200/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"6025\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/35baeeb8-b582-405e-2f46-178de16f8200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">PS会创建一个日志（过程「回放」），记录每场战斗。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">玩家保存日志以供日后研究、与朋友分享有趣的结果，或作为记录官方锦标赛结果的证明。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">PS的回放数据已经超过十年——足够的时间积累数百万个重放，比如下面的是10年前2014年的战斗回放。</span></span></p>\n  <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"294\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1158\" data-imgfileid=\"505100871\" data-ratio=\"0.5231481481481481\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f473ae0a-f706-4021-be3e-7497c1a0d800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2212\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f473ae0a-f706-4021-be3e-7497c1a0d800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">PS回放数据集是一个完全的、自然发生的人类数据集合，但这个数据集有个问题——这些数据是以第三方角度收集的，而不是第一人称，训练智能体需要用第一人称视角。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究团队通过将观众视角分别转换为每个玩家的视角来解锁PS回放数据集。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最终，研究团队搞出一个47.5万局真实人类对战组成的离线强化学习数据集，而且每天还在持续增长中。</span></span></p>\n  <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:48px;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"225\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1534\" data-imgfileid=\"505100870\" data-ratio=\"0.4\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2a11d5db-7c2c-4f0e-e035-548c647a3500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"3838\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2a11d5db-7c2c-4f0e-e035-548c647a3500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">在序列数据上使用离线强化学习算法训练</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">宝可梦拥有一个非常复杂的状态空间，因此在使用离线强化学习（offline RL）进行训练时，策略模型可能需要具备较大的规模和复杂的结构。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了使训练过程更加稳定，将这个问题转化为行为克隆（Behavior Cloning, BC）的角度来理解：预测一个人类玩家的动作，实际上是在尝试推理模仿的这个玩家的策略，以及他们对对手的理解。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了实现准确的预测，模型往往需要较长的上下文输入。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">强化学习（RL）在这种场景下的作用，是帮助我们从包含了不同水平玩家（包括竞技和休闲玩家）决策的大规模数据中，筛选出有效信息。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">采用的解决方案是actor-critic架构，其中critic的训练方式是使用标准的一步时序差分（temporal difference, TD）更新来输出Q值。至于actor的损失函数，其一般形式如下：</span></span></p>\n  <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1f892c8a-f930-4206-dc39-c21c814caf00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1414441147378833\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1011\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1011\" data-height=\"143\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"79\" data-imgfileid=\"505100875\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1f892c8a-f930-4206-dc39-c21c814caf00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"360\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"599\" data-imgfileid=\"505100876\" data-ratio=\"0.6399572649572649\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0d7736f3-4aec-42fc-38a3-4a2ec9607c00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"936\" data-width=\"936\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0d7736f3-4aec-42fc-38a3-4a2ec9607c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">接下来，需要为CPS（Competitive Pokémon Simulator）定义观测空间、动作空间和奖励函数。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">智能体需要获取足够的信息，以便能够模拟人类玩家的决策，而PS网站的用户界面是一个显而易见的参考点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不过，由于模型具备记忆能力，因此无需在每一个时间步都提供全部信息。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最终达成了一个折中方案：输入由87个文本词语和48个数值特征组成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">下图展示了数据集中一场回放中的示例。观测只包含对手当前上场的宝可梦。</span></span></p>\n  <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:48px;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/22e0abee-1d7d-403c-ce07-2c8aa8697800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3055555555555556\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1661\" data-height=\"508\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"172\" data-imgfileid=\"505100877\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/22e0abee-1d7d-403c-ce07-2c8aa8697800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">仅仅依靠强化学习能打赢人类吗？</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">传统做法教AI玩游戏，通常会设计规则、模拟状态、设计算法。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但这篇论文反其道而行之：直接喂数据</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，让它「模仿」人类怎么打。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他们训练了多个大小不同的智能体，从1500万参数的小模型，到2亿参数的大模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其中有的通过模仿学习训练（IL），有的则用离线强化学习（RL）进一步优化，还有的则加上「自我对战」的数据做微调。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b1de7ea8-8d01-4d5e-c138-d90b2867aa00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4981949458483754\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1662\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"288\" data-imgfileid=\"505100882\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b1de7ea8-8d01-4d5e-c138-d90b2867aa00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可以在Pokémon Showdown上观看各个模型的游戏重播。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e8cdb12e-23c7-4a3c-9240-c4c752487800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e8cdb12e-23c7-4a3c-9240-c4c752487800/public\"></span></strong></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">最强AI打上全球天梯前 10%</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">说了这么多，这AI真的能打吗？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究者将多个版本的模型送上Pokémon Showdown的天梯服务器——这是全世界宝可梦高玩集中的地方。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">结果模型居然排进了全球活跃玩家的前10%，并成功登上了排行榜。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在图中展示了Glicko-1阶梯分数及其评分偏差。柱状图标签标注的是GXE（胜率期望）统计数据。</span></span></p>\n  <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"238\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"690\" data-imgfileid=\"505100880\" data-ratio=\"0.42407407407407405\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/07bf1944-21d6-48ab-d091-c5c5e7654700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1627\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/07bf1944-21d6-48ab-d091-c5c5e7654700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">阶梯分位数（Ladder Percentiles），在 2025年2月至3月期间下载的回放数据中，共识别出14,022个在第1到第4世代活跃的用户名。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">以第1世代（Gen1）为例，在这些用户名中，有5,095个参与了 Gen1OU（标准对战规则），其中有2,661个活跃度较高，达到了在最终结果统计时拥有有效 GXE（胜率期望）数据的标准。</span></span></p>\n  <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"211\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1673\" data-imgfileid=\"505100881\" data-ratio=\"0.375\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/75150c91-f6f7-490d-dad5-9c30ee7de200/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"4464\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/75150c91-f6f7-490d-dad5-9c30ee7de200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这可能是你第一次听说有人用Transformer打宝可梦，还打赢了人类。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但从技术视角看，这背后是强化学习、模仿学习、大模型训练和数据重构的完整链路。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它不只是一个「有趣的实验」，更像是一次对数据驱动游戏 AI 的深度演练。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">下一步，或许可以不是打游戏，而是让AI玩转更复杂的现实任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此外，不同的训练策略以及大规模自我对战（self-play）技术，或许能够让智能体带来超越人类表现的突破。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://x.com/yukez/status/1909993963848622206</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://metamon.tech/</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2504.04395</span></span></section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "德州大学研究团队利用 Transformer 和离线强化学习，通过学习大量人类宝可梦对战数据，训练出在全球排名前 10% 的 AI 智能体，达到了人类顶级玩家的水平。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "德州大学研究团队利用 Transformer 和离线强化学习，通过学习大量人类宝可梦对战数据，训练出在全球排名前 10% 的 AI 智能体，达到了人类顶级玩家的水平。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了德州大学奥斯汀分校的研究团队如何使用 Transformers 和离线强化学习，训练出一个强大的宝可梦对战 AI 智能体。该智能体名为 Metamon，通过学习 47.5 万场人类对战回放数据，完全依赖数据学习，无需预设规则或启发式算法，便成功打入 Pokémon Showdown 全球排名的前 10%，达到了人类顶级玩家的水平。文章详细阐述了研究团队如何将第三方视角的对战数据转换为第一人称视角，以及如何设计观测空间、动作空间和奖励函数。实验结果表明，该方法在数据驱动的游戏 AI 领域具有巨大潜力，并可能应用于更复杂的现实任务，例如通过大规模自我对战技术实现超越人类的表现。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "离线强化学习结合 Transformer 可有效训练复杂游戏 AI，实现端到端的策略学习。",
      "explanation": "通过 Transformer 处理序列数据，离线强化学习从历史数据中学习策略，无需在线交互，降低了训练成本和风险。该方法完全依赖数据驱动，无需人工规则设计。"
    },
    {
      "point": "将第三方视角数据转换为第一人称视角是关键步骤。",
      "explanation": "为了让 AI 智能体更好地理解游戏状态和玩家决策，需要将观众视角的回放数据转换成每个玩家的视角。"
    },
    {
      "point": "数据驱动的 AI 在复杂任务中展现出巨大潜力。",
      "explanation": "该研究表明，通过学习大量真实数据，AI 可以掌握复杂策略，并在游戏中达到甚至超越人类水平。"
    },
    {
      "point": "该方法为数据驱动的游戏 AI 提供了一种新的研究范式。",
      "explanation": "通过纯数据驱动的方式，为游戏 AI 的研究提供了一个新的方向，摆脱了传统规则和启发式算法的限制。"
    },
    {
      "point": "下一步，或许可以不是打游戏，而是让 AI 玩转更复杂的现实任务。",
      "explanation": "该研究的意义在于，证明了 AI 可以通过学习大量数据来解决复杂问题，这为 AI 在现实世界中的应用提供了新的可能性。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "这不是那种靠搜索和规则的 AI，而是靠人类历史对战数据「喂出来」的智能体，能自己学着打。",
    "宝可梦对战融合了国际象棋般的长远策略规划、扑克牌那样充满未知信息和随机性，再加上足以填满一本百科全书的宝可梦、招式、特性和规则。",
    "这可能是你第一次听说有人用 Transformer 打宝可梦，还打赢了人类。",
